 have on particle\nacceleration in GRBs, and prospects for further testing these models with the\nanticipated data from HETE-2, Swift and GLAST.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Sep 2001 12:42:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
