der unity. Use of a\nreasonable volume (100's of cc) sample of this material at 50 mK and 10 kV/cm\nmight yield an electron EDM sensitivity of $10^{-33}$ e cm or better, a factor\nof $10^6$ improvement over current experimental limits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2001 22:14:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2001 19:32:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2002 22:36:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2002 18:02:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
